    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In Germany the concept is also not known which is also the reason de.wikipedia.org and the international commons.wikimedia.org disallow it. Seeing how minimally it is used on the English Wikipedia, I doubt this counts as citation and Section 4 sounds especially scary, because I guess our master server and @cncnet have far more players than the http://xwis.net/ platform which still sells keys.\n\nA better precedence is probably the other http://osgameclones.com/ which almost always avoid supplementing the proprietary game files. Actually this makes me wonder if we should shutdown all content mirrors.\n"
  },
