    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Content mirrors for the freeware games - TD, RA, TS - are fine. XWIS at our main games doesn't even matter, it's pre-RA2 playerbase died off before/around TFD got released, and CnCNet reached it's current playerbase on it's own.\n\nSection 4 only sounds scary for the abandoned/active games (D2K/RA2), but afaik D2K won't be downloaded via content mirrors - if yes, now that is a problem.\n\nOS Game Clones are again precedents for abandonware projects, not freeware ones.\n"
